<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Backend Geliştirme | İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --secondary: #a5b4fc;
      --accent: #fbbf24;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --card-bg: #fff;
      --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      --radius: 1.5rem;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      padding: 1.2rem 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .navbar .brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-right: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .navbar .menu a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu a::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      transition: width 0.3s;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar .menu {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar .brand {
        margin-right: 0;
      }
    }
    .hero-header {
      width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1 60%, #a5b4fc 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0 0 2rem 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
    }
    .hero-header .icon {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 24px #0004;
    }
    .hero-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .hero-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #e0e7ef;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s;
    }
    .badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .badge {
      background: var(--secondary);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 0.3em 1em;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .section-title {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }
    .content ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .content ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #6366f1;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .usage {
      background: var(--secondary);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="brand"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</a>
    <nav class="menu">
      <a href="/">Ana Sayfa</a>
      <a href="/dersler">Dersler</a>
      <a href="/katilimcilar">Katılımcılar</a>
      <a href="/denemeler">Denemeler</a>
      <a href="/hakkimda">Hakkımda</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-header">
    <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-server"></i></div>
    <h1>Backend Geliştirme</h1>
    <p>Node.js, Express ve modern backend teknolojileri ile sunucu tarafı geliştirme.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <a href="/dersler" class="back-link"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Tüm Dersler</a>
    <div class="badges">
      <span class="badge">Node.js</span>
      <span class="badge">Express</span>
      <span class="badge">REST API</span>
      <span class="badge">MongoDB</span>
      <span class="badge">JWT</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">Ders İçeriği</div>
    <ul>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Node.js Temelleri</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Express.js Framework</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> REST API Tasarımı</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Veritabanı Entegrasyonu</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Kimlik Doğrulama ve Güvenlik</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> API Dokümantasyonu</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="section-title">Nerede Kullanılır?</div>
    <div class="usage">
      <ul style="color:#fff;">
        <li><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Web Uygulamaları</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Mobil Uygulamalar</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> E-ticaret Sistemleri</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Veri Analizi Sistemleri</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Kurumsal Uygulamalar</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section-title">Açıklama</div>
    <p>Backend geliştirme, sunucu tarafında çalışan uygulamaların geliştirilmesini kapsar. Node.js ve Express.js gibi modern teknolojiler, hızlı ve ölçeklenebilir web uygulamaları geliştirmeyi sağlar. REST API'ler, veritabanı entegrasyonu ve güvenlik önlemleri, modern backend geliştirmenin temel bileşenleridir.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 